this is a python project, which draw chart using ascii char.

below is a example:

                                                                                
                                                                                
     +------------+    +------+                                                 
     |            |    |      |                                                 
     | box abcdef |<---+      |                                                 
     |            |    |      |                                                 
     +-----+------+    |      |                                                 
           |           |      |                                                 
           v           |      |                                                 
     +------------+    ++-----+                                                 
     |    box     |     |                                                       
     |     b      |     v                                                       
     +-----+------+   +---+                                                     
           |          |   |                                                     
           |          |   |                                                     
           |          |   |                                                     
           +--------->|   |                                                     
                      |   |                                                     
                      |   |                                                     
                      |   |                                                     
                      |   |                                                     
                      +---+                                                     